Ukrainian armed forces chief Valery Zaluzhnyi has announced that Russian forces used "Kinzhal" hypersonic missiles as part of the bombardment that struck targets across Ukraine on Thursday Morning. In a statement, Zaluzhnyi said 47 winged missiles were destroyed by the Ukrainian military, 20 of them in the area of the capital Kyiv. He added three out of four X-59 controlled air missiles "failed to achieve their goals". Zaluzhnyi stated: "The goal of the Russians remains unchanged - psychological pressure on Ukrainians and destruction of critical infrastructure. But we can not be broken!" PLEASE FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES